short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Print Client Extension to Manage Public Use Printers in Public Libraries.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Printing Extension for use with Libdata Time/Print Management Chrome APP - replaces Google Cloud Print, 
Used for Public Library Public Use Computers.

Adds two printers BW and Color to your Chrome Device. 

These two printers will automatically send printjobs to the Libdata Control Center Management Console.

You will need to install this if you are going to use Libdata's Print Management for Public Use Chrome Computers.

This extension must be used with the Libshield Chrome Client APP.

Utilizes IPP Printing from the Cloud Control Center.
